WorkItem.Description:
I'm not getting intellisense for the module when using Declaration Merging in a declaration file (*.d.ts) in TypeScript 0.9.1.1. 

__Example typing.d.ts:__
```
declare class MyModule {
    static debug: boolean;
}
declare module MyModule {
    class MyClass{
        static getStateFromNumber(width: number): MyClass.State;
    }
    module MyClass{
        enum State {
            one,
            two,
            three
        }
    }
}
```

__Intellisense should list:__
debug
MyClass

__Intellisense only gives:__
debug
